    • getParcelByZip

      public static java.io.File getParcelByZip​(java.io.File parcelIn, java.util.List<java.lang.String> vals, java.io.File fileOut) throws java.io.IOException
      Get parcels out of a parcel collection corresponding to a list of zipcodes Zipcodes are not directly contained in a field of the collection but is composed of two fields. Their values are set by default but it's possible to change them with the methods setCodeComFiled and setCodeDepFiled
      Parameters:
      parcelIn - input parcel collection
      vals - a list of zipcode values
      fileOut - file to export selected parcels
      Returns:
      a simple feature collection of parcels having the values contained in vals.
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException
